message:
We want to thank Erick Lorenzo and Yadira Granado from  Zo Creative, inc. for creating a new banner for us on such short notice. We appreciate their time and dedication to the project. 
We also want to thank South Jersey Speedpro Imaging for printing the banner last minute.  From NJ to FL there are great people working to help fight #ChildTrafficking. Thank you!
